    <lb n="1"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Νικίας</unclear> Ἀπολλωνίωι χαίρειν. ἔγραψας Λυσιμάχωι περὶ φυτῶν ὅπως 

    <lb n="2"/>δ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ι</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>υ. Λυσίμαχος μὲν οὖν ἔτυχεν ἐν Ἀλεξανδρείαι ὤν, 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">γὼ</unclear> δ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὲ</unclear> οῖς ἐλθοῦσιν περιαγαγ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὼν</unclear> πάντας τοὺς παραδείσους ἔδειξα 

    <lb n="4"/>ὅτι π<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αρ</unclear>᾽ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἡμῖν</unclear> χεύματα οὐκ ἔστιν οὐδ᾽ εἴωθεν γίνεσθαι, οὐκ ἠγνοοῦσαν δὲ 

    <lb n="5"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οὐδ</unclear>᾽ αὐτοί, ἀλλὰ ἐξ Ἀρσινόης τῆς νήσου μεταπεμπόμεθα, ἐκεῖ γὰρ ἔργωι 

    <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὕδ</unclear>ωρ ὑπάρχειν ἀεί, καὶ ἠξίουν κατα-

    <lb n="7"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σταλῆν</unclear>α<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ί</unclear>   παρὰ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σοῦ</unclear> πρὸς Λυσίμαχον, <choice><corr>ἐπόρισεν</corr><sic>επορισεγ</sic></choice> γὰρ ἂν αὐτοῖς ἐκ τῶν 

    <lb n="8"/>κάτω τόπων, οἱ δὲ ἔφασαν ἀρκεῖν αὐτοῖς ἐὰν λάβωσιν εἰς φυτείαν ἀπὸ τῶν 

    <lb n="9"/>παρ᾽ ἡμῖν ὑπαρχόντων. ἐδώκαμεν οὖν αὐτοῖς ὅσα ἠβούλοντο, ὧν τὸ καθ᾽ ἓν 

    <lb n="10"/>ὑ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">πογεγράφαμεν</unclear>. 

    <lb n="11"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="28">κη</num>, Ἁθὺρ <num value="25">κε</num>. 

    <lb n="12"/>σύκινα Χῖα, ἐρινεά, Λύδια, πραέα, <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">φο</unclear>ινίκεα, ὀλονθοφόρα· ῥόας ἀπυρήνου· 

    <lb n="13"/>μῆλ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear> ἐαρινά, καὶ τῶν διφόρων· καὶ ἀμπέλου καπνείου, Κιλικίας, Μενδαίου, 

    <lb n="14"/>Εὐ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δα</unclear>μιδε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ίου</unclear>, Μαρωνείου, κολοκυν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">θίνης</supplied>, <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">φο</unclear>ινίσσης, καπνείου, Ἀλεξανδρείου, 

    <lb n="15"/>βουμάστου, <gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>ερμύλου, δριμίος. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="16"/>Νικίου 

    <lb n="17"/>περὶ φυτῶν 

    <lb n="16"/>Ἀπολλωνίωι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.693" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.693" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" value="-0257-01-19" notBefore="-257" notAfter="-257">19. Jan. 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.693" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.693" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59033</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">693</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59033</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0092;1;59033" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.693" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.693" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">SB III 6785</bibl></div><div n="meta.693" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en" default="NO"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">C.C. Edgar, ASAE 23, 1923, S. 191.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr" default="NO"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon 